===============================================================
MELCO LGY-98 C-BUS Ethernet OS/2 NDIS 2.0.1 MAC driver ver.1.00
===============================================================

MELCO LGY-98 is a NE2000-compatible-like Ethernet Network Interface 
Card to insert NEC PC-98x1 C-BUS slots.
This driver is useless for the eComStation users, since NEC PC-98x1 
is not the PC/AT architecture:-)

Included files are:
lgy98.os2	NDIS 2.0.1 MAC driver
lgy98.nif	Network Information File
lgy98.sym	Symbol Map file
lgy98.lnk	Document (this file)
lgy98jp.lnk	Document (Japanese)
source.zip	Zip archive of source files


