2.Card resource configuration

No tool to configure the card resource on OS/2 Warp.
Use the DOS utility which is provided from MELCO. 

The website of MELCO: http://www.melcoinc.co.jp/ 
The driver/utility download page for LGY-98: 
 http://buffalo.melcoinc.co.jp/download/driver/lan/lgy-98.html


